1
00:00:23,110 --> 00:00:25,873
Regarding the upcoming projects for this year,

2
00:00:26,390 --> 00:00:31,966
In my opinion, we should bring in foreign investors.

3
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:38,260
I have already scouted several potential partners, as follows...

4
00:00:51,490 --> 00:00:52,046
Yes?

5
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:57,160
I don't mean to cross you.

6
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,000
But if this project is truly as important as you say,

7
00:01:01,590 --> 00:01:05,806
I think having your younger sister come in to help would lighten your load.

8
00:01:14,630 --> 00:01:15,446
That won’t be necessary.

9
00:01:16,970 --> 00:01:21,800
Once I turn 25 as stipulated in the will.

10
00:01:22,990 --> 00:01:26,153
I will have full authority to manage this company.

11
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:28,860
I don’t need anyone’s help.

12
00:01:31,670 --> 00:01:34,693
But you are only 24 right now, dear.

13
00:01:35,410 --> 00:01:38,240
And since your father granted me the authority to oversee things,

14
00:01:39,850 --> 00:01:45,400
I have the right to decide how we proceed.

15
00:01:49,110 --> 00:01:50,813
Does the Board agree?

16
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:57,560
Shall we let Ranya join in to prove her capabilities as well?

17
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:00,306
Don’t use my father to pressure me!

18
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:09,440
That sounds like a good idea.

19
00:02:09,466 --> 00:02:11,366
As heirs, both of you will have the chance to prove.

20
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:15,466
and for all who is more suited for the position of the next President.

21
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:24,653
In that case, I’ll take it that you’ve agreed, Chat

22
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:27,226
that you’ll allow your sister to compete as well.

23
00:02:35,850 --> 00:02:36,866
I agree.

24
00:02:47,950 --> 00:02:49,846
Ah... but...

25
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:53,773
I don’t know anything about the business yet.

26
00:02:55,666 --> 00:02:57,670
Could I please learn the ropes first?

27
00:03:00,090 --> 00:03:02,533
Let her continue with her duties for now.

28
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,720
Once I’ve learned enough,

29
00:03:09,290 --> 00:03:10,673
I’ll come back to challenge for the position.

30
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,586
Are you okay?

31
00:03:45,970 --> 00:03:46,633
Um.

32
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,413
Don’t get mad at me for poking my nose into your business...

33
00:03:49,850 --> 00:03:52,606
but today was dangerous as hell.

34
00:03:53,210 --> 00:03:55,666
It’s clear what that woman is up to,

35
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:58,846
she’s trying to kick you out and put her own daughter in your place.

36
00:03:59,950 --> 00:04:01,593
You need to watch your back, you know?

37
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:06,280
I’d like to see her try.

38
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:12,940
But Ranya promised me she’d stay by my side.

39
00:04:19,653 --> 00:04:21,650
Are you sure about that?

40
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:25,826
Think about it carefully, that’s her mother.

41
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:33,640
Here you go, dear.

42
00:04:34,646 --> 00:04:35,640
Thank you.

43
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,106
Are you tired,dear?

44
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:43,146
Not at all.

45
00:04:43,550 --> 00:04:45,213
I’m doing okay now.

46
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:50,500
You know... back when your dad and I were together,

47
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:54,933
I was looked down upon every single day.

48
00:04:58,106 --> 00:05:00,110
They called me low-class,

49
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:03,193
they called me a slut.

50
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:12,433
But now that I’m back here with you,

51
00:05:12,466 --> 00:05:17,020
I realize those insults meant nothing.

52
00:05:18,470 --> 00:05:20,733
Just having you is more than enough luck for me.

53
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:27,573
I’m so happy too,

54
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,440
that we’ve finally come back together.

55
00:05:33,290 --> 00:05:40,206
At first, I thought I’d never have a family like everyone else.

56
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:46,453
Thank you so much, dear.

57
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:50,586
I would do anything just to make you happy.

58
00:05:52,513 --> 00:05:54,893
Because, we’re family.

59
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,040
I’ll do the same for you, Mom.

60
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:07,666
so, could you help me out by being the face of me?

61
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:14,140
I’m not saying you have to snatch Pimchat’s position away from her…

62
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:17,440
I just want you to have a real presence in the company

63
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,606
But if you do well,

64
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:27,966
I’m sure your older sister would be very proud of you.

65
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:32,426
You two are very close, aren’t you?

66
00:06:35,210 --> 00:06:36,193
Please dear.

67
00:06:40,530 --> 00:06:41,453
Yes, Mom.

68
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:08,753
Open it and look!

69
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:15,333
I’m asking you seriously, did you always do such sloppy work back when you were a student?

70
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:17,473
I gave you plenty of time.

71
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:21,613
Did you think just because you’re an intern, you can do whatever you want?

72
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:26,146
This kind of work damages the company!

73
00:07:26,890 --> 00:07:27,826
I’m sorry, but...

74
00:07:27,866 --> 00:07:29,566
You’re going to talk back to me?

75
00:07:29,593 --> 00:07:30,666
- Am I your friend?
- What’s going on here?

76
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:35,420
K’Tina, honestly,

77
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:37,880
I’m not okay with this intern.

78
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:41,486
I gave her the assignment a long time ago,

79
00:07:41,513 --> 00:07:44,306
and she just keeps getting it wrong, over and over. It’s constant mistakes and constant revisions!

80
00:07:44,346 --> 00:07:45,280
So, I….

81
00:07:45,306 --> 00:07:46,593
No, but…

82
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:49,553
"But" what?

83
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:50,926
You messed up, and then you.

84
00:07:50,953 --> 00:07:52,453
That’s enough, Jane.

85
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:54,820
She gets it now.

86
00:07:54,873 --> 00:07:57,500
You should head back to your desk.

87
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:58,700
I’ll handle this myself.

88
00:07:59,910 --> 00:08:02,133
Yes,please do.

89
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:13,866
Oh, look at you acting all pouty now.

90
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:17,413
You don't put up a fight with others, but you love to fight with me.

91
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,413
That’s completely different!

92
00:08:27,490 --> 00:08:31,193
How so? Honestly,

93
00:08:32,053 --> 00:08:33,173
look at our ranks,

94
00:08:33,430 --> 00:08:36,160
I’m way higher up than she is,

95
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:39,533
and you talk back to me every chance you get.

96
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,166
Are you just here to rub it in?

97
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:43,780
Fine, I’m going back to work.

98
00:08:43,806 --> 00:08:44,346
Hey, wait.

99
00:09:01,570 --> 00:09:08,660
I’m trying to tell you to never bow your head to anyone if you aren't wrong.

100
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:12,966
even if that person is your boss.

101
00:09:17,306 --> 00:09:18,706
Want to try doing it my way?
